&lt;li&gt;Work with our clients and internal users to gather, synthesize, and prioritize user feedback&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate closely with engineers, designers, data scientists, and our research team to scope requirements and guide product development from conception to launch.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Translate complex user needs and technical capabilities into clear product specifications and actionable development tasks.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Demo new product features to clients, develop product marketing materials, and clearly articulate the value of our tools.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop a deep understanding of the progressive political ecosystem to ensure our product strategy anticipates and meets the most pressing needs of our users.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
